preference.name: CATIA_volume_mass_ply_bl_prop
preference.preference_description: Name of the property type string of the GDE BOM Line corresponding to the Ply in CATIA and used to store CATIA mass volume information of the corresponding ply. The default value will be used if the property specified does not exist, if it is not a string type or if it corresponds to the value of the preference CATIA_material_ply_bl_prop
